	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9798701751008><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj>What to put training points into?</span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jan 19th 2:12 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Okay, so we've worked out from experience that putting training points into weapon or casting skills is a waste, and that for a wizzy there's no trade skill thats really worth the time it takes.<br><br>So, I have to ask, seeing as I've been storing TP's for a while now, what should a sound minded wizzy spend their points on? For the life of me I can't think of anything...<br><br>Any suggestions?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
